Description: 6 fragments of papyrus. Demotic text in black and red on 3 (temple ritual: hymn to Thoth/Iah-Thoth from Dimeh/Soknopaiou Nesos to judge by hand), painted vignettes on two showing a sun god and a fecundity figure on 2.
Bibliographic references: Trismegistos / An interdisciplinary portal of papyrological and epigraphic resources (129007) (http://www.trismegistos.org/text/129007)
Stadler 2021 / Iah-Thot und der solare Schöpfergott. Fragmente einer Sammlung von Thot-Hymnen (Papyrus British Museum EA 76126)
